fields.description:
APPCELERATOR STUDIO OVERHEATS MY MACBOOK PRO & RANDOMLY QUITS 20 times a day: "application not responding" or "out of memory error has occurred" or FORCE QUIT. I can't work for more than 5 minutes without this happening! 5 seconds glitch when I scroll code or open new file, so frustrating!! Please help!

UPDATE 7: This has been happening for 2 months straight now for every Appcelerator Studio version up to date. Use XCODE!

UPDATE 6: Appcelerator studio overheats my macbook pro.....I had to buy a mat cooler for my laptop because Appcelerator Studio makes it overheat. Use XCODE!

UPDATE 5: Appcelerator studio constantly says "application not responding and quits on me" all the time. I have to "force quit" the application at least 20 times a day, no exaggeration whatsoever. Use XCODE!

UPDATE 4: For anyone who has this issue, check to make sure you are updated to the latest Java version. this works for about 5 minutes but DID NOT fix my issue. Use XCODE!

UPDATE 3: I had to buy 1 Terrabyte of storage and ran Appcelerator Studio off of it in order for it to run faster. ALTHOUGH, there are still memory issues and Appcelerator Studio randomly closes the workspace because of an error. (See screen shots below) Use XCODE!

UPDATE 2: I had to buy a mat cooler for my laptop because Appcelerator Studio makes it overheat. Use XCODE!

UPDATE 1: I AM SWITCHING TO XCODE IMMEDIATELY! Appcelerator Studio is impossible to work with because it is slow and glitchy! Use XCODE!

Appcelerator Studio is SO SLOW on my Macbook Pro. I have 8 G of memory available. Appcelerator Studio takes 3-5 seconds just to scroll through my code or open a new file! This is crazy! Any advice!?!

Others also have this issue: https://community.appcelerator.com/topic/740/appcelerator-studio-editor-is-obscenely-slow-while-i-m-writing/3
